rComments: She is probably one of my favorite Accy professors. Her classes are usually short and to the point. Daily in-class exercises are useful so don't skip class. She is very approachable and willing to help students go over the material. There is a term project. Do NOT put it off till last minute.

Very good teacher. Laid back and willing to help. Doesn't overwhelm students but gives you the necessary knowledge to master important course material and do well on tests if you put the time in to study.
GREAT TEACHER!!  I WISH I HAD HER IN ALL MY OTHER ACCOUNTING TEACHERS HERE.
